00:47:34.780 --> 00:47:35.460
Prof: Okay.
 

00:47:35.460 --> 00:47:37.297
If the books were written
anonymously how did the names

00:47:37.297 --> 00:47:38.659
that are associated with
them…

00:47:38.659 --> 00:47:46.030
Student: 
&gt;

00:47:46.030 --> 00:47:51.338
Prof: Yeah,
most of the stuff that we'll

00:47:51.338 --> 00:47:55.039
say has a wrong name attached in
the New Testament is not

00:47:55.039 --> 00:47:57.550
anonymous, although there are
some.

00:47:57.550 --> 00:47:58.639
It's pseudonymous.
 

00:47:58.639 --> 00:48:00.268
But there are some that are
anonymous, too.

00:48:00.268 --> 00:48:02.780
The gospels we say are
anonymous, because they didn't

00:48:02.780 --> 00:48:05.050
come attached with a name,
as far as we know.

00:48:05.050 --> 00:48:07.360
How did those names get
attached?

00:48:07.360 --> 00:48:10.206
By different people--partly it
was because they wanted this

00:48:10.206 --> 00:48:12.170
text to be authoritative in some
way,

00:48:12.170 --> 00:48:15.585
and so they tended to attach
the name of a particular apostle

00:48:15.585 --> 00:48:17.579
to them or a particular
disciple.

00:48:17.579 --> 00:48:18.902
Or in some ways,
for example,

00:48:18.902 --> 00:48:21.360
the Gospel of Luke may have
gotten its name Luke,

00:48:21.360 --> 00:48:22.989
because in the Acts of the
Apostles,

00:48:22.989 --> 00:48:24.909
which is also written by the
same author,

00:48:24.909 --> 00:48:28.219
Luke is an actual character who
follows Paul around.

00:48:28.219 --> 00:48:31.034
So it may have been that the
name Luke and the Acts of the

00:48:31.034 --> 00:48:33.800
Apostles got connected with the
acts of the apostles,

00:48:33.800 --> 00:48:35.949
and the Gospel of Luke as its
author.

00:48:35.949 --> 00:48:37.672
So sometimes,
it's something in the text

00:48:37.672 --> 00:48:40.059
itself that may have prompted
someone to think that.

00:48:40.059 --> 00:48:42.105
Often, we just don't know how
it got it, and it just happened

00:48:42.105 --> 00:48:43.980
because somebody just said,
"It's authoritative.

00:48:43.980 --> 00:48:45.230
It must've been written by an
apostle."

